Distributed Crawler

Scheduler Node: manage all worker nodes, send task to worker node
Worker Nodes: receive task from scheduler node, and submit new task to scheduler node.


Scheduler Node:
    URL manager: manage URLs, and pass url to worker node
    data extraction:
    Data Storage: read data returned from worker node, and extract URL to URL manager, store title and short description.
    Schedule


worker nodes:
    scheduler
    HTML downloader
    HTMl Parser